# Tests
/test/ @acme/qa
*.spec.js @acme/qa
*.test.js @acme/qa

# Tooling / CI
/.github/ @acme/platform
/scripts/ @acme/platform
*.yml @acme/platform

# Docs
/docs/ @acme/docs
*.md @acme/docs
README.md @acme/docs
